divs: sighting detailsi was driving from lakefield towards bridgenorth on eighth line just past burckhorn rd. when a white flash in the sky caught my attention. i looked up and seen a circle with a piece missing from it. best way to describe it is it looked like a cookie with a bite taken out of it or like a 3\4 moon. it's entire surface flashed bright white and then the light disappeared and it shot forward at a speed i had never seen before, it was almost instantly out of sight like it had never been there. my mind did not want believe what my eyes were seeing, i was stunned.
Summary: Like a 3/4 moon, or a perfect circle with a bite taken out of it.
